  "title": "Xtra Garlicky Spanish Tomato Gazpacho",
  "description": "A garlicky and cozy Spanish dish featuring unsweetened cocoa and bhuna, served in a Korean brass bowl, this gazpacho is perfect for a cold evening, with a cheese-pull that will leave you wanting more.",
