      "amount": "1 cup",
      "notes": "diced"
    },
    {
      "name": "Cucumber",
      "amount": "1 cup",
      "notes": "diced"
    },
    {
      "name": "Manchego Cheese",
      "amount": "1 cup",
      "notes": "shredded"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a blender, combine diced Roma tomatoes, minced garlic, unsweetened cocoa, and bhuna spice mix.",
    "Blend the mixture on high speed until smooth.",
    "Heat olive oil in a saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add diced red onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the blended tomato mixture to the saucepan and stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in diced cucumber.",
    "Serve the gazpacho hot, topped with shredded Manchego cheese.",
    "Place the gazpacho in a Korean brass bowl for serving."
  ],
